<style>
          *{
                    margin: 0;
                    padding: 0;
                    outline: none;
                    box-sizing: border-box;
          }
          html{
                    width: 100%;
                    height: 100%;
          }
          body {
                    width: 100%;
                    height: 100%;
          background-image: url(http://imageshack.com/a/img911/3424/qMyVHf.jpg);
          background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }
        
        div{
          height: 550px;
          width: 875px;
          text-align: justify;
          font-family: 'Amatic SC', cursive;
          font-size: 30px;
        }
        
        #main-head {
          text-align: Center;
          font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
          font-size: 60px;
        }
        
        .more {
          display: none;
          border-top: 1px solid #666;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #666;
        }
        
        a.showLink,
        a.hideLink {
          text-align: center;
          font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
          font-size: 22px;
          text-decoration: none;
          color: #FFC0CB;
          background: transparent url('down.gif') no-repeat left;
        }
        
        a.hideLink {
          background: transparent url('up.gif') no-repeat left;
        }
        
        a.showLink:hover,
        a.hideLink:hover {
          border-bottom: 1px solid #FFC0CB;
        }</style>
<body>
          
  <header id="main-head" class="TYhead" color="white"><font color="white">
          <h5>Thank You, Dudes!</h5></header>
          
          <a href="#" id="example-show" class="showLink" onclick="showHide('example');return false;">See more</a>
       
        
      <div id="example" class="more">
        <p>
          Kevin, <br>
          <br> Thank you very much for the opportunity to interview for a developer position Friday. <br>
          It was great to meet you and some fellow students to speak further about the position.
